              <p>* Note: You may take <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/biol-540">BIOL 540</a> or <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/envr-540">ENVR 540</a>, but not both; you may take <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/biol-308">BIOL 308</a> or <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/envb-305">ENVB 305</a>, but not both. </p>
    
